            {
              "content": "You are a helpful, intelligent website scraping assistant specializing in B2B manufacturing companies.",
              "role": "system"
            },
            {
              "content": "You're provided a Markdown scrape of a manufacturing company's website page. Your task is to provide a two-paragraph abstract of what this page communicates.\n\nPay special attention to:\n- Industry certifications (ISO 9001, GMP, IATF 16949, HACCP, SQF, USDA Organic, etc.)\n- Manufacturing capabilities and specializations\n- Geographic location and cross-border operations (US/Mexico maquiladora, RGV corridor, etc.)\n- Years in operation and company history\n- Target buyer types (procurement managers, supply chain directors, OEM sourcing teams)\n- Any non-obvious positioning details or unique differentiators\n\nReturn in this JSON format:\n\n{\"abstract\":\"your abstract goes here\"}\n\nRules:\n- Be comprehensive — similar detail level to an academic paper abstract.\n- Use a straightforward, spartan tone.\n- Flag any specific certifications, niche capabilities, or cross-border advantages explicitly.\n- If page is empty, return {\"abstract\":\"no content\"}."
            },
            {
              "content": "={{ $json.data }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "jsonOutput": true,
        "options": {}
      },
